    <string name="repair_regex_help_body">Use Java named capture groups to extract date parts from file names.\n\nRequired groups: year, month, day\nOptional groups: hour, minute, second\n\nExample pattern:\n(?&lt;year&gt;\d{4})(?&lt;month&gt;\d{2})(?&lt;day&gt;\d{2})[_-](?&lt;hour&gt;\d{2})(?&lt;minute&gt;\d{2})(?&lt;second&gt;\d{2})\n\nMatches file names like:\n  MyBackup_20240315_142500.jpg\n  photo-20231201-093045.png</string>
